# Bug: Expense Images Not Displayed After Upload

## Module
Add Expense

## Platforms
- Android
- iOS

## Description
Uploaded or scanned images for expenses are not displayed within the app. Only the image title or placeholder is visible, preventing users from verifying uploaded receipts.

## Steps to Reproduce
1. Navigate to Add Expense screen  
2. Upload or scan an image  
3. Save the expense  
4. View the saved expense  

## Expected Result
- Uploaded/scanned image should be visible  
- Users should be able to preview the image  

## Actual Result
- Only the image title or placeholder is shown  
- Image is not displayed  

## Severity
High

## Priority
High

## Impact
- Users cannot verify expense receipts  
- Reduces trust in the application  
- Affects financial record accuracy  

## Notes
Possible issue with image rendering or storage mapping
